# ProposalGenius — MVP Walkthrough

## What Was Built

ProposalGenius is a fully functional AI-powered document generation platform. It runs as a single-page app from the file `proposalgenius/index.html` — **no server or installation required**.

---

## Features

| Feature | Status | Details |
|---|---|---|
| Signup / Login | ✅ | Any email + password (demo) |
| 6 Document Templates | ✅ | All FREE — no tier gates |
| AI Generation | ✅ | Groq `llama-3.1-8b-instant` |
| Edit + Preview Tabs | ✅ | Markdown editor + live render |
| PDF Export | ✅ | Professional A4, no watermark |
| AI Detection | ✅ | Custom Groq analysis prompt |
| Plagiarism Check | ✅ | Originality baseline scan |
| Dashboard & Stats | ✅ | Usage counts + document list |
| LocalStorage Persistence | ✅ | Sessions + documents saved |

---

## How to Use

1. **Open** `c:\Users\Kashif\Documents\Zain this\proposalgenius\index.html` in any modern browser
2. **Sign up** with any email + password (4+ chars)
3. **Generate** → pick a template → fill title and details → click **✨ Generate with Groq AI**
4. Switch to **Preview** tab to review formatted output
5. Click **💾 Save Document** — you'll be taken to the document viewer
6. From the viewer, click **Export PDF** or run **AI Detection** / **Plagiarism Check**

